{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_06_01",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 1話 ドキドキ温泉旅行",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございまーす",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　遙子さん、今日はオフでしたよね？\nひょっとして、休みなのに何も予定がないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Haruko-san‚ you're off today‚ right?\nBy any chance‚ you don't have any plans for your day off?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと何その言い方！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ what kind of way is that to say it!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "べ、別にやることがなくて暇を持て余したから\n事務所に顔を出した訳じゃないわよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-It's not like I had nothing to do and\njust came to the office because I was bored!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "こう見えても私にはお友達が沢山いて\n休みの日はみんな私と遊びたいって引っ張りだこに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though it may not seem like it‚ I have lots of friends‚\nand on my days off‚ everyone wants to hang out with me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ。自分で言ってて虚しくなってきちゃったわ\nええ、そうよ。本当は予定がなくて暇だったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…sigh. I feel empty even saying that.\nYes‚ that's right. I really didn't have any plans and was bored.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "オフに誰とも遊ぶ予定がなくたっていいでしょ！\n一人は寂しいから事務所に来たっていいでしょ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay not to have plans with anyone on a day off‚ right?\nIt's okay to come to the office because I'm lonely and alone‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "誰も責めてませんよ。それに、遙子さんの\n予定が空いていてむしろ助かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No one is blaming you. Besides‚ Haruko-san‚\nit actually helps that you're free today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "助かったってどういうこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean by 'it helps'?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん……\n今から俺と温泉旅館に行って一泊してもらえませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san…\nCould you come with me to a hot spring inn for an overnight stay‚ starting now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ！？　急にそんなこと言われても\n二人きりで、しかも宿泊するだなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? I can't just agree to something like that all of a sudden.\nJust the two of us‚ and staying overnight…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "二人きりじゃないですよ。旅館にいるスリクスから\n緊急事態だと連絡があったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not just the two of us.\nI got an emergency call from IIIX at the inn.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "俺一人で対処出来るか分からないので\n遙子さんが一緒に来てくれると心強いんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not sure if I can handle it alone‚\nso I'd feel more secure if you could come with me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.6719441731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "あ……そういうことだったのね……\nドキドキして損しちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… so that's what it was about…\nI got nervous for nothing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.3719441731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ドキドキ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nervous?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7052775065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんでもないから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's nothing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.1052775065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "それより、問題が解決したら\n私も温泉を満喫していいのよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "More importantly‚ once the issue is resolved‚\nI can enjoy the hot springs too‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.3052775065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです。宿代も事務所から出るので\n終わったら好きなだけ温泉を楽しんで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. The lodging is covered by the office‚\nso feel free to enjoy the hot springs as much as you want after it's over.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.5052775065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことなら、喜んで付き合うわ\n温泉旅行なんて楽しいオフになりそうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ in that case‚ I'm happy to join.\nA hot spring trip sounds like a fun time off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.1386108398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "それで、行くのは私と\n{user}君の二人だけなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So it's just me and\n{user}-kun going?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.1052775065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、芽衣も誘うつもりです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I'm planning to invite Mei as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.1386108398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "だったら、誤解されないように\n誘う時は言い方に気をつけなきゃダメよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ to avoid misunderstandings‚\nyou have to be careful about how you invite someone‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.7386108398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "さっきは私だったから良かったけど\n他の子には、先に事情を説明すること。いいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was okay this time because it was me‚\nbut with other girls‚ make sure to explain the situation first. Got it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.6719441731,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8766.66666669999,
          "startTime": 137.4386108398
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい。気をつけます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I’ll be careful…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.4386108398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（なんだか遙子さんの様子が変だったけど……）\n（誤解されないようにってなんのことだ？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Haruko-san was acting a bit strange though…）\n（What did she mean by avoiding misunderstandings?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.4052775065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その日の午後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ㅡㅡThat afternoon",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.7386108398,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1400.0000000000057,
          "startTime": 148.1386108398
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.3719441731
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.3719441731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "やっと旅館に着きましたね\nあれ？　芽衣は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've finally arrived at the inn.\nHuh? Where's Mei…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.4386108398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.6719441731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃんなら「ここが温泉旅館！？　すごーい！」\nって目を輝かせて飛び込んで行ったわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei-chan was like 'This is a hot spring inn!? Wow!'\nand darted in with shining eyes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.8386108398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.2719441731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "あっという間で止める暇もなかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She was so quick‚ I didn't even have time to stop her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.2719441731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣らしいな……\n俺達もスリクスが泊まってる部屋に急ぎましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's so Mei…\nLet's hurry to the room where IIIX is staying.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.2719441731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.5719441731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、スリクスさんから詳しい話を聞かないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ we need to hear the full story from IIIX…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.5719441731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん？　緊張してるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san? Are you nervous?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.6052775065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.9719441731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "ええ……\nスリクスさんとはまだちゃんと話したことがないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes…\nI haven't really had a proper conversation with IIIX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.1386108398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 183.9052775065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、彼女達って少し壁があるでしょ？\n怖いって言うか……近寄りがたいオーラがあるのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know‚ they seem a bit unapproachable‚ right?\nKind of intimidating… have this aura that keeps people at a distance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.6386108398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "私達と仲良くする気はないみたいだし……\n打ち解けられる自信がないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like they don't want to be friend with us…\nI'm not confident we can break the ice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.4386108398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.0719441731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか？　俺は遙子さんなら彼女達と星見プロの\n架け橋になれると思いますけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so? I think Haruko-san could be the bridge between\nthem and Hoshimi Prods…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.3386108398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 206.7386108398
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてそう思うの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why do you think so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.7386108398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "昔、慣れない仕事でいっぱいいっぱいになっていた\n新人の俺に、遙子さんはよく声を掛けてくれましたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back when I was overwhelmed with unfamiliar tasks as a newbie‚\nHaruko-san‚ you often reached out to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.6719441731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 215.9052775065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちが落ち着くようにハーブティーを入れてくれたり\n俺の愚痴を嫌な顔一つせずに聞いてくれたり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You calmed me down with herbal tea‚\nlistened to my complaints without showing any annoyance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 219.0719441731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "優しくて気配りが出来る遙子さんがいてくれたから\n俺は星見プロにすんなり馴染むことが出来たんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to your kindness and thoughtfulness‚\nI was able to blend into Hoshimi Pro smoothly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.9386108398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 229.4052775065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk023.m4a",
      "text": "……ずるいわ。そんな風に言われたら\n出来ないなんて言えないじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's not fair. When you put it like that‚\nI can't say I can't do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.6052775065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 234.9719441731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-hrk024.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ないわね\nこの旅行中に打ち解けられるように頑張ってみるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess I have no choice.\nI'll try my best to break the ice during this trip.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 237.2052775065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫ですよ、スリクスのみんなも遙子さんになら\nきっと心を開いてくれます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry‚ I'm sure the members of\nIIIX will open up to you‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.0386108398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数十分後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ㅡㅡ A half hour later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.1052775065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 248.8386108398
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
