      "text": "幽霊よりも、ギスギスしてる三人の方が怖かったわ\nあの中に入って打ち解けるなんて絶対無理だから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The vibes of them were scarier than any ghost\nThere's no way I can blend in with them!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 258.8719441731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "そこをなんとか。優しくて気配りが出来て包容力がある\n遙子さんならきっと出来ます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please try. With your kindness‚ attentiveness‚ and empathy‚\nHaruko-san‚ you can surely do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 266.9719441731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 269.1052775065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
