      "text": "悪いけど、うまく交流出来る自信がないわ\n三人ともギスギスしてて本当に怖かったんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ but I don't have the confidence to interact well with them.\nAll three of them were so tense‚ it was truly frightening.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 281.0386108398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_06_01-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "そう言わずに、お願いします\nお礼はちゃんとしますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ I'm asking you.\nI'll make it up to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 287.8719441731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenroom-00-noon.webp",
